In Menu:
--------------------------------------------
Movement Keys: 	D-pad		Navigate
Confirm Key:		A			OK/ Use/ proceed to next step
Cancel Key:		B			Cancel / Back
(I)nventory:		Start		Exit menues
Scroll up:		R-trigger		next pane (magic, stats, etc.)
Scroll down:		L-trigger		next pane (magic, stats, etc.)		
(L)ook Key:		X			
Quick KEy:		Y			

