In Dungeon:
--------------------------------------------
Movement Keys: 	D-pad		move if open, open door if closed, attack if enemy
Confirm Key:		A			attack enemy, open/close door, use object, disarm trap
Cancel Key:		B				quick command 1?
(I)nventory:		Start		inventory
Scroll up:		R-trigger		scroll message log
Scroll down:		L-trigger		scroll message log		
(L)ook Key:		X			view tile/thing
Quick KEy:		Y				quick command 2?











